title: Blazing 5 - Week 9
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 9
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and RJ go over in week 9:


Colts @ Steelers

Lions @ Raiders

Browns @ Broncos

Packers @ Chargers

Patriots @ Ravens


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast.
